{
  "texts": [
    "The content that has been rejected recently has a lower rank.",
    "However, if multiple clients from changed interfaces send negative feedback about the rejected content, it also leads to a reduction in its rank.",
    "Fig. 13 Interest-Key Binding (IKB) process",
    "The rank will be higher if multiple users express interest in the same content and there is no negative feedback.",
    "However, the given scheme is strongly reliant on the feedback of the client."
  ]
}